omspite-gitz/#Venomous-Valuables" style="color:#fefefe">Venomous Valuables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Glinty-Gubbinz-that-Troggoths-Found" style="color:#fefefe">Glinty Gubbinz that Troggoths Found</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Spell-Lores" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">S</b>pell Lores</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Lore-of-the-Moonclans" style="color:#fefefe">Lore of the Moonclans</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Lore-of-the-Spiderfangs" style="color:#fefefe">Lore of the Spiderfangs</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Jaws-of-Mork-Allegiance-Abilities" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">J</b>aws of Mork Allegiance Abilities</a><img class="tooltip logo2" title="White Dwarf’07/20 Jaws of Mork (2th edition)" src="/aos/img/expansions/WhiteDwarf_logo2.png"></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Battleplans" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attleplans</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#An-Unfortunate-Location" style="color:#fefefe">An Unfortunate Location</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Path-to-Glory" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>ath to Glory</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Gloomspite-Gitz-Warband-Tables" style="color:#fefefe">Gloomspite Gitz Warband Tables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Retinue-Gobbapalooza-and-Hero-Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Retinue, Gobbapalooza and Hero Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Champion Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/gloomspite-gitz/#Troggoth-Arachnarok-and-Big-Stuff-Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Troggoth, Arachnarok and Big Stuff Followers Rewards Table</a></div></div></span></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_4.png" style="width:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_7.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_6.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_5.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
